{"tid":2314144,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"深入淺出–動物過冬的一道奇謀","createTime":"2020-12-06T10:26:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-06T23:53:45.000Z","uid":38861,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9fe28b8b0cc17dbd2e1a094e68b01c52496a6df0","tid":2314144,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T10:26:46.000Z","msg":"冬天到來，各動物均出盡渾身解數迎接大自然給予的挑戰，譬如老生常談的燕子南遷及松鼠冬眠等等。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/88Q2WQ8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F88Q2WQ8.jpg&h=2f5ab46a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖2）而今次將要介紹的主角，就是體積非常細小的小臭鼩(Etruscan shrew)。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bMsQmhQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbMsQmhQ.png&h=0ffb0853&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖3）冬天期間，小臭鼩(Etruscan shrew)的大腦皮層厚度會相應減少。<br />\n從圖中可見，唯獨是L4區域有所縮細，其他區域並無顯著改變。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MdQ2WRc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMdQ2WRc.png&h=9efa3c83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖4）有趣的是，在夏天期間，若果食物供應不足夠的話，小臭鼩(Etruscan shrew)的大腦皮層厚度亦會相應減少。<br />\n但若果食物供應足夠的話，則不會出現「腦細」的情況。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XXhQmhV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXXhQmhV.png&h=a87dc35e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖5）之所出現「腦細」的其中一個原因，相信是與新陳代謝有關。<br />\n對比其他區域，L4區域含有最高濃度的Cytochrome oxidase(CO)蛋白酶，<br />\n而CO蛋白酶的功用則為製造能源。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YxpjeCY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYxpjeCY.png&h=4d0070a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這暗示出可能小臭鼩為了應對冬天食物短缺問題，所以索性盡量棄用與新陳代謝有關的部份，以作節省資源。<br />\n<br />\n當然，亦不排除有其他的可能性。<br />\n<br />\n（圖6）圖中為大腦皮層磁力共振得出的影像。<br />\n藍綠色為冬天的時候，而橙黃色則為夏天時候。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1bmmsX1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1bmmsX1.png&h=c07b4ede&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n冬天和夏天的影像互相重疊後，橙黃色的區域較多，顯示夏天的腦部體積較冬天的為大。<br />\n<br />\n平均來說，小臭鼩在冬天時候的大腦皮層厚度會縮減28%左右，但在下一年夏天的時候則會完全恢復回原有的厚度。<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去<span class=\"teal\">Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單</span>俾一個<span class=\"green\">like</span>以及<span class=\"red\">Bookmark</span>，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=PkQR3zmsNSOm8whbchxq2vG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=0d408c30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「<span class=\"orange\">買一嚿/半嚿薯仔</span>」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=PkQR3zmsNSOm8whbchxq2vG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=4944cd49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n有興趣接收科學資訊的話，歡迎follow IG: potatopigtongue。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/potatopigtongue/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fpotatopigtongue%2F&d=PkQR3zmsNSOm8whbchxq2vG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=ab0f8367\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/potatopigtongue/</a><br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.pnas.org/content/early/2020/11/24/1922888117\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pnas.org%2Fcontent%2Fearly%2F2020%2F11%2F24%2F1922888117&d=PkQR3zmsNSOm8whbchxq2vG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=25a2b40d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pnas.org/content/early/2020/11/24/1922888117</a>"},{"pid":"7a22870fd680c427fd00562447b8cc4da7974571","tid":2314144,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T10:31:30.000Z","msg":"支持樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b50a4c81c65f8e69207c685e641c95a2ea9ea41a","tid":2314144,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7a22870fd680c427fd00562447b8cc4da7974571","tid":2314144,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T10:31:30.000Z","msg":"支持樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T10:35:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />thx"},{"pid":"a2e162c06c08a7479c1d3d9839b2acd00b2146e1","tid":2314144,"uid":316927,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T10:36:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e343dee6662e1d336f5a8959ac110d0182153ff6","tid":2314144,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T10:37:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e8f203fe681ab17749fab88bb3fade0b092bcee","tid":2314144,"uid":150982,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T10:37:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出多d"},{"pid":"2b3c01134a5b8c9f4c2454a9cf2912d4ac4f5858","tid":2314144,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T10:58:18.000Z","msg":"已經大過我個腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"371bd7d000aace64d1cfc487cdfc36b077e0af7b","tid":2314144,"uid":244368,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T11:47:30.000Z","msg":"樓豬有無諗過出廣東話科普書<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 